steps.name: Click on the 'Library' button from the sidebar menu
Click on the first form from the Bookmark page
Click on the 'Next' button on the 'New transaction' modal
Click on the 'Associated client' drop-down field
Enter client name into the 'Search' field for associated clients
Click on the 'Transaction type' drop-down field
Select the 'New business' option from the 'Transaction type' drop-down field'
